<p>This workshop was organised to finalise plans for the next major release of NeuroML: <a href="alpha_schema">version 2.0</a>.
    It was held on Thus 31st Mar & Fri 1st Apr 2011 at UCL's <a href="http://www.ucl.ac.uk/efd/roombooking/building-location/?id=126">SSEES Building</a> and the
<a href="http://www.londonhouse.org.uk/functionrooms/churchillroom/">Churchill Room</a> at Goodenough College in London. Local Organisers were Angus Silver and Padraig Gleeson.</p>

